<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;If a contract is terminated under this section, CMS cannot enter into a new contract or service area expansion in the PDP region or regions served by the contract with PDP Sponsor or with an organization whose covered persons, as defined in 42 CFR § 423.508(f), also served as covered persons for the terminating PDP Sponsor for a period of up to 2 years unless there are circumstances that warrant special consideration, as determined by CMS.&quot;">
