<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;CMS and PDP Sponsor, an entity that has been determined eligible to operate a Voluntary Medicare Prescription Drug Plan by the Administrator of CMS under 42 CFR § 423.503, agree to the following for the purposes of §§ 1860D-1 through 1860D-43 (with the exception of §§ 1860D-22(a) and 1860D-31) of the Social Security Act (hereinafter referred to as 'the Act').&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
