</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;If PDP Sponsor does not intend to renew its contract, in accordance with 42 CFR § 423.507(a)(2), it must notify: (a) CMS in writing by the first Monday of June in the year in which the current contract period ends; (b) Each Medicare enrollee, at least 90 days before the date on which the nonrenewal is effective. PDP Sponsor must provide, to enrollees, through this notice or outbound telephone calls, information on alternatives available for obtaining qualified prescription drug coverage within the PDP region, including Medicare Advantage Prescription Drug plans, Medicare cost plans offering a Part D plan, and other PDPs, and&quot;">
