  <data key="d3">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A PDP Sponsor that chooses not to renew its contract with CMS."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a8d49cc5f599bfb3f6f139071bb0cfac</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SUBSIDIARY OF THE APPLICANT'S PARENT ORGANIZATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A subsidiary entity under the same parent company as the applicant, which must also not be offering Part D benefits."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-647561dd6831e3ae72c2d43faf5b0b9f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;QUALITY ASSURANCE PROGRAMS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PROGRAM"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Programs designed to monitor and ensure the quality and safety of Part D services."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-89bdab9933b704535281ee7396b3c0c8</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PRINT DISTRIBUTION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ACTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The dissemination of formulary data through physical media, permitted under the license."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b14ea02aabc3c1d74ff07de937978aa9</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;COVERED PERSONS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Covered persons are individuals who served in a role for a PDP Sponsor as defined in 42 CFR § 423.507(a)(4)."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a8d49cc5f599bfb3f6f139071bb0cfac</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;42 CFR § 423.505(B)(27)&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"REGULATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Federal regulation requiring new PDP Sponsors to pass an essential operations test."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-647561dd6831e3ae72c2d43faf5b0b9f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;COMPLAINTS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Formal grievances or issues reported to CMS regarding the PDP Sponsor’s performance or services."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-89bdab9933b704535281ee7396b3c0c8</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;OTHER MEANS OF DISTRIBUTION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ACTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Any additional method of distributing formulary data, permitted under the license."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b14ea02aabc3c1d74ff07de937978aa9</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;42 CFR § 423.507(A)(4)&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"REGULATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A federal regulation that defines who qualifies as a covered person."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a8d49cc5f599bfb3f6f139071bb0cfac</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SUBPART M OF 42 CFR PART 423&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"REGULATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Federal regulation governing coverage determinations, grievances, appeals, and formulary exceptions for Medicare Part D."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-647561dd6831e3ae72c2d43faf5b0b9f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CONFIDENTIALITY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The requirement for the PDP Sponsor to protect the privacy of enrollee information as mandated by 42 CFR § 423.136."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b14ea02aabc3c1d74ff07de937978aa9</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SPECIAL CONSIDERATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Special consideration refers to circumstances that may allow exceptions to the 2-year restriction."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a8d49cc5f599bfb3f6f139071bb0cfac</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;COVERAGE DETERMINATIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PROCESS"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The process by which a PDP Sponsor evaluates whether a medication is covered under a plan."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-647561dd6831e3ae72c2d43faf5b0b9f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ENROLLEE RECORD ACCURACY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The obligation to ensure that records of Medicare beneficiaries are accurate and up to date."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b14ea02aabc3c1d74ff07de937978aa9</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PLAN BENEFIT PACKAGES (PBPS)&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PLAN"</data>
  <data key="d4">"PBPs are the benefit structures offered by a PDP Sponsor."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a8d49cc5f599bfb3f6f139071bb0cfac</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;GRIEVANCES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PROCESS"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Formal complaints from beneficiaries about plan services or decisions."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-647561dd6831e3ae72c2d43faf5b0b9f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;TRUE OUT-OF-POCKET COSTS&quot;">
