<node id="&quot;CONTRACT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"DOCUMENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A contract between CMS and a PDP Sponsor that governs the terms of Part D plan offerings and can be terminated by CMS under 42 CFR § 423.509."&lt;SEP&gt;"A contract between the PDP Sponsor and CMS that can be modified or terminated by mutual written consent."&lt;SEP&gt;"A contract is a formal agreement between the PDP Sponsor and CMS."&lt;SEP&gt;"A formal agreement between the PDP Sponsor and CMS, effective from the signature of CMS's authorized representative until December 31, 2025, with potential for renewal."&lt;SEP&gt;"A legally binding agreement between the PDP Sponsor and the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services."&lt;SEP&gt;"The contract is deemed to incorporate statutory changes and implementing regulations during its term."&lt;SEP&gt;"The legal agreement between CMS and the PDP Sponsor, incorporating the 2025 Solicitation and other regulatory materials."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a1ba6b4dc9d71dff813e0972c4e6c371&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-acb96757aadb929819265d4fddd43c2d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a8d49cc5f599bfb3f6f139071bb0cfac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bb09bdd246d7da48cb03f821334b1a33&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a77fb65c6800edbf628ea7f71f893ea5</data>
