</node>
<node id="&quot;42 CFR PART 423&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"REGULATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A federal regulation that provides detailed rules for Medicare Part D, including contract terms and compliance."&lt;SEP&gt;"Federal regulations governing the Medicare Part D Prescription Drug Benefit, excluding Subparts Q, R, and S."&lt;SEP&gt;"Federal regulations governing the Medicare Part D Prescription Drug Benefit."&lt;SEP&gt;"This regulation governs the operation of Medicare Prescription Drug Plans, excluding Subparts Q, R, and S."&lt;SEP&gt;"This regulation outlines CMS's responsibilities in overseeing the Medicare Prescription Drug Plan."</data>
