  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"FINANCIAL TRANSACTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Payments made by the PDP Sponsor to pharmacies for services rendered to beneficiaries."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-089a3e7f57f00ea7d36a53726e96e60c</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;45 CFR PARTS 160, 162, AND 164&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"REGULATORY DOCUMENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Regulations under HIPAA that govern the privacy, security, and administrative simplification of health information."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a77fb65c6800edbf628ea7f71f893ea5</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;COST SHARING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Cost sharing refers to the portion of enrollment-related costs that are shared between the PDP Sponsor and CMS, as defined by 42 CFR § 423.6."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b14ea02aabc3c1d74ff07de937978aa9</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;42 CFR § 423.104(B)&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"REGULATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A specific regulation prohibiting discrimination in beneficiary enrollment under Medicare Part D."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98acde792b4efcfd60a0e94224e24870</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;42 CFR&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"REGULATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A federal code that includes regulations governing Medicare Part D, including reimbursement policies."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-089a3e7f57f00ea7d36a53726e96e60c</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ENROLLMENT RELATED COSTS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Enrollment related costs are expenses associated with enrolling beneficiaries in the Medicare Part D program, which the PDP Sponsor is required to share with CMS."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b14ea02aabc3c1d74ff07de937978aa9</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DISCRIMINATION IN BENEFICIARY ENROLLMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The act of treating beneficiaries unfairly based on characteristics such as age, health status, or other protected factors."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98acde792b4efcfd60a0e94224e24870</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;FEDERAL STATUTES AND REGULATIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"LEGAL FRAMEWORK"</data>
  <data key="d4">"All other applicable federal laws and rules that the PDP Sponsor must comply with."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a77fb65c6800edbf628ea7f71f893ea5</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BENEFICIARY PREMIUMS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"FINANCIAL CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The premiums paid by Medicare Part D beneficiaries, which the PDP Sponsor is required to calculate and collect accurately."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-89bdab9933b704535281ee7396b3c0c8</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CMS'S AUTHORIZED REPRESENTATIVE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d4">"An individual authorized by CMS to sign the contract, marking its effective date."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a77fb65c6800edbf628ea7f71f893ea5</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;42 CFR § 423.6&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"REGULATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A federal regulation outlining the fees and cost-sharing requirements for enrollment-related activities."&lt;SEP&gt;"A federal regulation under Title 42 of the Code of Federal Regulations, Section 423.6, which governs the cost-sharing responsibilities of PDP Sponsors in the Medicare Part D program."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-089a3e7f57f00ea7d36a53726e96e60c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b14ea02aabc3c1d74ff07de937978aa9</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ENROLLMENT APPLICATIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ACTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The submission of forms or requests by individuals to join a Medicare Part D plan."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98acde792b4efcfd60a0e94224e24870</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;42 CFR §§ 423.286 AND 423.293&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"REGULATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Federal regulations that govern the calculation and collection of beneficiary premiums under Medicare Part D."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-89bdab9933b704535281ee7396b3c0c8</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DECEMBER 31, 2025&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"DATE"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The end date of the initial contract term."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a77fb65c6800edbf628ea7f71f893ea5</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;REIMBURSEMENT STANDARD&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A standard used by the PDP Sponsor to determine pharmacy reimbursement based on drug cost, which must be updated at least every 7 days."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b14ea02aabc3c1d74ff07de937978aa9</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;INDIVIDUALS WHO CHANGE THEIR ELECTION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Beneficiaries who switch their Medicare plan during the open enrollment period."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98acde792b4efcfd60a0e94224e24870</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;42 CFR § 423.294&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"REGULATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A federal regulation requiring the PDP Sponsor to identify incorrectly collected amounts and repay any additional amounts due."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-89bdab9933b704535281ee7396b3c0c8</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;42 CFR § 423.506&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"REGULATORY DOCUMENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Regulation that governs the renewal of the contract for successive one-year periods."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a77fb65c6800edbf628ea7f71f893ea5</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DRUG COST&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The cost of a prescription drug, which serves as the basis for the reimbursement standard used by the PDP Sponsor."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b14ea02aabc3c1d74ff07de937978aa9</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;OPEN ENROLLMENT PERIOD&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"TIME PERIOD"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A designated time each year when Medicare beneficiaries can change their health plans."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98acde792b4efcfd60a0e94224e24870</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;INCORRECTLY COLLECTED AMOUNTS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"FINANCIAL CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Funds collected by the PDP Sponsor that are found to be erroneous and must be identified and refunded."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-89bdab9933b704535281ee7396b3c0c8</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;42 CFR § 423.507&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"REGULATORY DOCUMENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Regulation that determines the qualification of the PDP Sponsor to renew the contract annually, contingent on not providing a nonrenewal notice."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a77fb65c6800edbf628ea7f71f893ea5</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;MARKET PRICE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The current price of a drug in the marketplace, which the PDP Sponsor must reflect in its reimbursement standards."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b14ea02aabc3c1d74ff07de937978aa9</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;MEDICARE ADVANTAGE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PROGRAM"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A Medicare program that offers health coverage through private insurance companies."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98acde792b4efcfd60a0e94224e24870</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ADMINISTRATIVE AND MANAGEMENT CAPABILITIES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CAPABILITY"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The organizational capacity required for the PDP Sponsor to effectively manage financial, communication, benefit administration, and quality assurance functions related to Part D services."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-89bdab9933b704535281ee7396b3c0c8</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;NONRENEWAL NOTICE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"LEGAL ACTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A formal notice submitted by the PDP Sponsor to CMS indicating intent not to renew the contract, which disqualifies the sponsor from renewal."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a77fb65c6800edbf628ea7f71f893ea5</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;7 DAYS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"TIME PERIOD"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The maximum interval between updates to the reimbursement standard, requiring at least one update every 7 days."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b14ea02aabc3c1d74ff07de937978aa9</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;42 CFR § 422.62(A)(3)&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"REGULATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A regulation describing the open enrollment period for Medicare Advantage beneficiaries."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98acde792b4efcfd60a0e94224e24870</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;FINANCIAL ACTIVITIES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ACTIVITY"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Activities related to managing funds, including budgeting, accounting, and premium handling, required for Part D service delivery."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-89bdab9933b704535281ee7396b3c0c8</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ARTICLE VII&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONTRACT SECTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A section of the contract that outlines the conditions under which the PDP Sponsor may choose not to renew the contract."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a77fb65c6800edbf628ea7f71f893ea5</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;JANUARY 1&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"DATE"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The starting date for the initial update of the reimbursement standard each year."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b14ea02aabc3c1d74ff07de937978aa9</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;42 CFR § 423.38(E)&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"REGULATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A regulation requiring PDP Sponsors to accept enrollment applications from individuals changing their election during the open enrollment period."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98acde792b4efcfd60a0e94224e24870</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;COMMUNICATION ACTIVITIES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ACTIVITY"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Functions involving information exchange with beneficiaries, CMS, and other stakeholders, required for Part D service delivery."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-89bdab9933b704535281ee7396b3c0c8</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SUBPART F OF 42 CFR PART 423&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"REGULATORY DOCUMENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A section of federal regulations that governs the bidding process for the contract renewal."&lt;SEP&gt;"Federal regulation governing bid submission and review for Medicare Part D."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-647561dd6831e3ae72c2d43faf5b0b9f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a77fb65c6800edbf628ea7f71f893ea5</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PRESCRIPTION DRUG PRICING STANDARD&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A standard used to determine the price of prescription drugs for reimbursement purposes, which may not be publicly available."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b14ea02aabc3c1d74ff07de937978aa9</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BASIC PRESCRIPTION DRUG COVERAGE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"BENEFIT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The core prescription drug coverage required under Medicare Part D."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98acde792b4efcfd60a0e94224e24870</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BENEFIT ADMINISTRATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ACTIVITY"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Processes related to enrolling beneficiaries, managing benefits, and ensuring compliance with Part D rules."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-89bdab9933b704535281ee7396b3c0c8</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BID&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A formal proposal submitted by a PDP Sponsor outlining premiums, benefits, and cost-sharing for the upcoming year."&lt;SEP&gt;"A proposal submitted by the PDP Sponsor for contract renewal, which must be accepted by CMS."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-647561dd6831e3ae72c2d43faf5b0b9f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a77fb65c6800edbf628ea7f71f893ea5</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;INDIVIDUAL DRUG PRICES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Specific prices for each prescription drug that must be disclosed by the PDP Sponsor to pharmacies if the pricing standard is not publicly available."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b14ea02aabc3c1d74ff07de937978aa9</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;42 CFR § 423.100&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"REGULATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A regulation defining the basic and supplemental prescription drug benefits under Medicare Part D."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98acde792b4efcfd60a0e94224e24870</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;QUALITY ASSURANCE ACTIVITIES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ACTIVITY"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Programs and procedures to ensure the quality and accuracy of Part D services."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-89bdab9933b704535281ee7396b3c0c8</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SUBPART N OF 42 CFR PART 423&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"REGULATORY DOCUMENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A section of federal regulations that provides appeal procedures, which do not apply to bid agreement failures."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a77fb65c6800edbf628ea7f71f893ea5</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PHARMACIES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Entities that dispense prescription drugs to Medicare beneficiaries and receive reimbursement from the PDP Sponsor."&lt;SEP&gt;"Pharmacies that receive advance disclosure of individual drug prices from the PDP Sponsor for use in claim reimbursement."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-089a3e7f57f00ea7d36a53726e96e60c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b14ea02aabc3c1d74ff07de937978aa9</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SUPPLEMENTAL BENEFITS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"BENEFIT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Additional prescription drug benefits beyond the basic coverage, as defined in 42 CFR § 423.100."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98acde792b4efcfd60a0e94224e24870</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;42 CFR § 423.505(B)(25)&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"REGULATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A federal regulation specifying the minimum administrative and management capabilities required of a PDP Sponsor to deliver Part D services."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-89bdab9933b704535281ee7396b3c0c8</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;NONRENEWAL&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"LEGAL ACTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The act of the PDP Sponsor choosing not to renew the contract at the end of its term."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a77fb65c6800edbf628ea7f71f893ea5</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;REIMBURSEMENT OF CLAIMS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ACTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The process by which pharmacies are paid for dispensed drugs, based on updated drug prices disclosed by the PDP Sponsor."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b14ea02aabc3c1d74ff07de937978aa9</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SUBPART C OF 42 CFR PART 423&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"REGULATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A section of 42 CFR Part 423 that outlines the structure and requirements for Part D benefits."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98acde792b4efcfd60a0e94224e24870</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;MANUFACTURER DISCOUNTS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"FINANCIAL CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Discounts provided to beneficiaries on prescription drugs from drug manufacturers, required to be offered by the PDP Sponsor."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-89bdab9933b704535281ee7396b3c0c8</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;REQUIRED TIMEFRAMES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The specific deadlines by which the PDP Sponsor must submit a nonrenewal notice."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a77fb65c6800edbf628ea7f71f893ea5</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ELECTRONIC CLAIM&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
